message.body: I'm working at 445 tomorrow so I'll be done at 115

Okay! Mike is going to go to lunch with his sister tomorrow. I'm sure he'll meet me somewhere.
You want lunch? Or did you eat? Go somewhere? Otherwise, I'll just get fish and rice.
Let's go get some lunch today. I was gonna ask you. We always on the same page my sister
Hahahaha. We're just so good. Where you wanna go?
I picked last time.
Is it bad that I wanna go to the noodle house? Haha
PSHAW! No!
Leggo!
Sooo I'm sorry to say but I will not be sticking to the whole no meat thing this Friday. Lol what's the point in yaki tori boy if I can't eat meat
Haha. It's cool! I won't judge you. God will. Jesus will. The Holy Spirit will. But you'll get no judgement from me!
Lol I can deal with that
Did you decide whether you're going to your class tomorrow? Lol
I probably will. Only because I have to go to the lab again tomorrow. Most likely. If I somehow get out of it, I might not. Haha
I'll walk to you after work
K
I just went to old navy and bought the softest pants and shirt EVER!
Did you leave yet?
Yeah I'm on my way
Okie. Lemme know when you're close.

Yeah I think so haha
